      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition. The exterior shows minor wear consistent with normal use, with no significant scratches, dents, or rust. The paint retains good color and gloss. The interior is clean with moderate use evident on the upholstery and trim. Mechanical systems are functioning properly with no known issues.",
